{"tid":845073,"cid":19,"subCid":0,"title":"絲打入，你地會揀大學毒撚定ive型男？","createTime":"2018-10-02T11:13:41.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-03T13:34:17.000Z","uid":71508,"like":5,"dislike":48,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"75ea8d7b32e4339f2a2b16fac58b7e46539f93fa","tid":845073,"uid":71508,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-02T11:13:41.000Z","msg":"我同女神都係讀ive<br />\n但我知最近女神同一個中大仔行得好埋 <br />\n<br />\n但我同女神關係都唔算好生疏啦 <br />\n成日見面都會講野 <br />\n連我生日女神都記得會係facebook同我講生日快樂!! <br />\n仲有我問女神去唔去細o camp 女神都話會去!! <br />\n我係咪點都有d優勢?? 至少 中大仔無得黎過夜 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n我自認係靚仔樣..唔算好差姐? 都叫五官端正丫.. <br />\n但我係facebook search到個中大仔..d相望落都好鬼毒撚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n真心認真 你地估女神會揀邊個 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n論前途同錢途 我點睇都唔會輸啦係咪先...<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n另外 --- 絲打們你地會揀 靚仔定大學生?? <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"60fc0882e4dc8a80956454d325d466ba9c98e205","tid":845073,"uid":210081,"like":9,"dislike":1,"score":8,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-10-02T11:18:07.000Z","msg":"貼張圖睇下你係咪型男先再討論啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7bcb11965c0f3af1cf22143f0e328f939a7d3181","tid":845073,"uid":187076,"like":7,"dislike":19,"score":-12,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-02T11:18:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/10/02/191812_7637149e571553e974a27d4c62e52997.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.ne